  "body": "[comment]: # (Please replace ... with your information. Remove < and >)\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Feature or Bug? i.e Type: Bug)\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Describe the feature you would like, or briefly summarise the bug and what you did, what you expected to happen, and what actually happens. Sections below)\r\n*Summary*:   2 Accounts were created on real devices.\r\na) \r\nStatus version: 0.9.21\r\nOperating System: Android 6.0.1\r\nCel Phone and Model: Galaxy J7 Prime SM-C610M\r\n\r\nb)\r\nStatus version: 0.9.21\r\nOperating System: Android 7.0\r\nCel Phone and Model: Galaxy J7 Prime SM-610M\r\n\r\nAccount on (A) was renamed to Luis Garcia\r\nAccount on (B) was renamed to Luis Test\r\n\r\nAccount B Started a 1-1 Chat with Account A by reading Accounts A contact code image, from this point a new chat opens but it shows on Account B's chat that Accounts A's name is \"Impractical Passionate Hart\" while on Account A, Accounts B's name is Luis Test. \r\n\r\nAlso when viewing the user profile on Account B's that Accounts A's name is \"Impractical Passionate Hart\"\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n[comment]: # (Describe what you expected to happen.)\r\nCorrect name should be shown on both sides of the 1-1 Chat after rename.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n[comment]: # (Describe what actually happened.)\r\nThe Contact Code for Accounts does not seem to be updating after name change and keeps original name when reading image to start chat.\r\n\r\nView from Device A\r\n![screenshot_20180705-174548](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1890179/42458912-a41cc6ac-834f-11e8-823c-dbeb69d176f6.png)\r\n\r\nView Device A Profile from Device B\r\n![photo from luis garcia](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1890179/42459043-e4b6a764-834f-11e8-9fc7-572598390b9c.jpg)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\n\r\nThese steps consist of using 2 devices.\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n-